txt.en: Chief Ora of the Leijona-heimo tribe of the Lumi-väki

Rejoice!

Kaj of the Lumi-väki
known as Warg-skinner, Claw-wearer, Plague of the Susi-väki, and Spearer of the Ancient Mursu
son of Chief Ora of the Lumi-väki

and

Pinja of the Lumi-väki
called Jä-maven and Stalker of the Kalpa-kita
sister to Etu, Ikka, and Manu


wish you to join them in celebration of their union.

The night of the next half-moon has been deemed auspicious.
Food, drink, and warmth will be provided.

Offerings may be placed at Vesi-paistâ in their name.
